            Torus 
            </div>
            <div class="mytext">
            All about torus<br>
            </div>
            <div class="cen">
            $\mbox{Parametric form}$
            \begin{align}
            &\textit{x}=(\textbf{R}+\textbf{r}*\cos{\alpha})*\cos{\beta}\\
            &\textit{y}=(\textbf{R}+\textbf{r}*\cos{\alpha})*\sin{\beta}\\
            &\textit{z}=\textbf{r}*\sin{\alpha}\\
            \end{align}

            $\mbox{Close form}$ 
            \begin{align}
            (x^2 + y^2 + z^2 + R^2 - r^2)^2 = R^2(x^2 + y^2) \\
            \end{align}
            <img src="../image/torusred.png" width="60%" height="60%" /><br>
