            <div class="mytext">
            Sphere Equation<br>
            </div>
            <div class="cen">
            <img src="../image/sphere_equation.png" width="40%" height="40%" /><br>
            </div> 
            Derived Sphere Parametric Equation<br> 
            We slices the sphere to different slices according to hight<br>  
            e.g. $z = 0, z = 0.2, z = 0.5$<br>
            \begin{align*}
            \begin{split}
            r'&= r\cos(\theta) \\
            r'&= \sin(\beta) \\
            x &= r\cos(\theta)\cos(\beta) \\
            y &= r\cos(\theta)\sin(\beta) \\
            z &= r\sin(\theta) \\
            
            \end{split}
            \end{align*}





